<text><body>
<lb n="0030b03"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0030b04"/>
<lb n="0030b05"/>
<lb n="0030b06"/><head type="no">No. 924B</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0030b07"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0030001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】享保年間刊豐山大學藏本，【甲】保延三年寫高山寺藏本，【乙】高山寺藏古寫本</note>藥師如來念誦儀軌一卷</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0030b08"/>
<lb n="0030b09"/><byline type="Translator">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智
<lb n="0030b10"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0030b11"/><p>佛一時在維那離<note n="0030002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音樂＝樂音【甲】</note><app n="0030002"><lem>音樂</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">樂音</rdg></app>樹下。與<note n="0030003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大菩薩）&M062403;＋三【原】</note><app n="0030003"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">大菩薩三</rdg></app>萬六千
<lb n="0030b12"/>比<note n="0030004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">丘＋（八萬）&M062403;【原】</note><app n="0030004"><lem>丘</lem><rdg wit="【？】" resp="【原】">丘八萬</rdg></app>人俱。及十二神王。并諸眷屬天龍八部
<lb n="0030b13"/>大神王。在如是等大眾會中。說是法已。大眾
<lb n="0030b14"/>皆聞無不歡喜。是<note n="0030005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">即名＝名即【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030005"><lem>即名</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">名即</rdg></app>為結願神&CB00057;。即薄伽
<lb n="0030b15"/>梵說&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0030b16"/><p type="dharani">南謨薄伽筏帝鞞殺<note n="0030006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">社＝耶【乙】</note><app n="0030006"><lem>社</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>寠嚕蔽&CB00222;璃&CB00425;唎婆
<lb n="0030b17"/><note n="0030007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">喝＝羯【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030007"><lem>喝</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">羯</rdg></app>囉闍耶怛他揭<note n="0030008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多＋（耶阿羅歇帝三藐三勃陀耶）【乙】</note><app n="0030008"><lem>多</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">多耶阿羅歇帝三藐三勃陀耶</rdg></app>怛姪他唵鞞殺<note n="0030009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逝＋（鞞殺逝）【乙】</note><app n="0030009"><lem>逝</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">逝鞞殺逝</rdg></app>鞞
<lb n="0030b18"/>殺社<note n="0030010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">三沒＝沒哩【乙】</note><app n="0030010"><lem>三沒</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">沒哩</rdg></app>揭帝<note n="0030011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＝沙【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030011"><lem>婆</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">沙</rdg></app>婆呵</p>
<lb n="0030b19"/><p>若有受持此真言。能拔身中過去生死一切
<lb n="0030b20"/>重罪。不復經歷三<note n="0030012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">塗＝途【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030012"><lem>塗</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">途</rdg></app>。免離九橫超越眾<note n="0030013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">苦＋（七佛經并陀羅尼集經有此三字）【乙】</note><app n="0030013"><lem>苦</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">苦七佛經并陀羅尼集經有此三字</rdg></app></p>
<lb n="0030b21"/><p>根本印真言。以左右<note n="0030014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔手〕－【乙】</note><app n="0030014"><lem>手</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>頭指以下八指。反
<lb n="0030b22"/><note n="0030015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔叉〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030015"><lem>叉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>入於掌。以二大指來去&CB00057;曰</p>
<lb n="0030b23"/><p type="dharani">唵戰馱祇<note n="0030016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哩＋（二合）夾註【乙】</note><app n="0030016"><lem>哩</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">哩<note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app><note n="0030017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝沙【甲】</note><app n="0030017"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">沙</rdg></app>婆呵</p>
<lb n="0030b24"/><p><note n="0030018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔次〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030018"><lem>次</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>結<note n="0030019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔護〕－【乙】</note><app n="0030019"><lem>護</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>讚</p>
<lb n="0030b25"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0030020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（曩莫）＋薩【甲】</note><app n="0030020"><lem>薩</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">曩莫薩</rdg></app>縛勃馱曩薩縛爾<note n="0030021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曩＝奈【乙】</note><app n="0030021"><lem>曩</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">奈</rdg></app><note place="inline">入</note>迦盧拏怛麼<note place="inline">二合平</note>
<lb n="0030b26"/>迦訶羅<note n="0030022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔引〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030022"><lem><note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>&CB00418;迷<note place="inline"><note n="0030023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">存＝在【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030023"><lem>存</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">在</rdg></app>念於我</note>俱嚕吠女哩也<note place="inline">二合</note>入縛
<lb n="0030b27"/>羅<note place="inline">引</note><note n="0030024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（入縛羅）＋怛【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030024"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">入縛羅怛</rdg></app>他&CB00344;<note n="0030025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">多麼訶捺＝哆訶摩捨【乙】</note><app n="0030025"><lem>多麼訶捺</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">哆訶摩捨</rdg></app>耶<note place="inline"><note n="0030026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（辯才）＋成【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0030026"><lem>成</lem><rdg wit="【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">辯才成</rdg></app>就義</note>曩謨悉羯羅
<lb n="0030b28"/><note place="inline">歸命頂禮義</note></p>
<lb n="0030b29"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>藥師<note n="0030027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔如來念誦〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030027"><lem>如來<note n="0030028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔念誦〕－【乙】</note><app n="0030028"><lem>念誦</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>儀軌<note n="0030029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔一卷〕－【甲】</note><app n="0030029"><lem>一卷</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0030030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">甲本奧書曰保延三年五月十八日已時許執筆，同時一校了，後世菩提出離生死因也，同年七月二日酉時點了</note></jhead></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>
